 <h1>BoxSmart API</h1>
 <div class="subtitle">AI-Assisted Box Selection System — Complete 5-Section Technical Blueprint</div>
 <div class="highlight-box">
  <p><strong>Hiring Assignment Overview:</strong> This document lays out the full architecture and source code for the Box Selection automation microservice. The solution leverages deterministic algorithmic screening (Volume, Weight, and Bounding Box aspect evaluations) to find the most cost-efficient shipping container.</p>
 </div>
 
 <h2>Section 1: Project Setup &amp; Database Schema</h2>
 <p>To initialize the module, dependencies are installed and a clean relational structure isolating entities is built using precise numerical abstractions (<code>DecimalField</code>) to eliminate floating-point precision flaws.</p>
 
 <h3>File: <code>box_selector/models.py</code></h3>
